node.text:
Ray tracing and DLSS are coming to #WatchDogsLegion!

Take a tour of near-future London’s vibrant neighborhoods with #RTXOn in our exclusive new trailer powered by GeForce RTX.

node.title: Ray Tracing and DLSS Come to Watch Dogs: Legion

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by NVIDIA GeForce on September 09, 2021. May be an image of outdoors and text that says '39 FPS DLSS DLSSOFF OFF ま 82 FPS DLSS DLSSON ON RTX OFF RTX ON'.
